Fowler, who finished in the top five at every major championship this year, hinted that the 'task force' would have some lively discussions over the direction US golf needs to take to avoid future embarrassment.

And he admitted one thing Mickelson would surely echo: 'It sucks losing'.

'I am looking forward to getting together with the guys to see what everyone has to say,' saifd Fowler.

'Clearly, we want to win the Cup, and it is not as if there has been a lack of motivation or anything like that. It sucks losing. Everyone is aware of that and everyone wants to win.'

 

